<text id="02-output-contract" title="Agentic RAG Iterative Retrieval Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="700" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the iterative-retriever-config artefact + valid/invalid examples.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/agentic-rag-iterative-retrieval.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["max_iterations", "judge_model", "generator_model", "dedup_by_chunk_id", "drift_threshold", "sanitise_chunks"],
  "properties": {
    "max_iterations": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 5},
    "judge_model": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^(haiku|sonnet|gpt-5-mini|gemini-flash)"},
    "generator_model": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^(opus|sonnet|gpt-5|gemini-pro)"},
    "dedup_by_chunk_id": {"type": "boolean", "const": true},
    "drift_threshold": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.0, "maximum": 1.0},
    "sanitise_chunks": {"type": "boolean"}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item id="f1">max_iterations &gt;5 (rule r1)</item>
      <item id="f2">judge_model == generator_model (rule r2 + fm-01)</item>
      <item id="f3">dedup_by_chunk_id=false (rule r3)</item>
      <item id="f4">drift_threshold &lt;0.5 or &gt;0.95 (rule r4)</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "max_iterations": 3,
  "judge_model": "haiku",
  "generator_model": "opus",
  "dedup_by_chunk_id": true,
  "drift_threshold": 0.7,
  "sanitise_chunks": true
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "max_iterations": 12,
  "judge_model": "opus",
  "generator_model": "opus",
  "dedup_by_chunk_id": false,
  "drift_threshold": 0.0,
  "sanitise_chunks": false
}
]]></code>
    <note>max_iterations &gt;5 (f1); judge==generator (f2); dedup off (f3); drift_threshold too low (f4); sanitise off invites prompt injection.</note>
  </example>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-agentic-rag-iterative-retrieval.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
